          "Pass Effect": {
            "text": "The creature seems to mean you no harm. Although communicating is difficult, you ask her for help in navigating K'n-Yan (-1). If you pass, she serves as your guide; place 1 Eldritch token on the active Mystery. If you fail, you wander long caverns; move to an adjacent space and become Delayed.",
