          "Pass Effect": {
            "text": "The creatures that the serpent people have created are horrific, and you resist the urge to look away (-1) If you pass, you learn the forgotten truths of Yoth; place 1 Eldritch token on the active Mystery. If you fail, you cover your eyes and wait for the nightmare to be over; lose 2 Sanity.",
