            ]
          },
          "Pass Effect": {
            "text": "You find several drawings on the cave wall that represent Tsathoggua. As you examine them, you are attacked by amorphous creatures made of viscous, black slime (-1). If you pass, you fend off the creatures and can learn the story of the toad god; place 1 Eldritch token on the active Mystery. If you fail, lose 2 Health.",
            "links": [
